snippet.title: [DOAXVV] New Venus Release! Introducing Tsukushi
snippet.description:
A new Venus "Tsukushi" (CV: Maria Sashide) has arrived in "DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation!"
Enjoy the beginning of a new Vacation with the "timid", "gloomy girl" who really likes "Venuses" and "manga".

○Official Site：https://game.doaxvv.com/en/lp.html
○Facebook：https://www.facebook.com/doaxvvstaff/
Game Information
○Title：DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation
○Platform：Windows PC (Steam,Johren) 
○Genre：Sports Vacation
○Release Date：Steam 10 April 2019 (Wednesday), Johren 1 July 2021 (Thursday)
○In-game purchases：Free to play/In-game purchases in Steam,Johren
○hashtag：#DOAXVV
